---

<PageLayout title={metaTitle} description={metaDescription} heroPage={true} lang="fr">

  <!-- Hero: full-bleed dark -->
  <section class="relative bg-[var(--color-surface-dark)] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0">
      <img src="/images/hero-china-migration.webp" alt="" class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover" loading="eager" decoding="async" />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0f0f12]/90 via-[#0f0f12]/70 to-[#0f0f12]/30"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-[#0f0f12]/80 to-transparent"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <!-- Breadcrumbs -->
      <nav aria-label="Fil d’Ariane" class="pt-20 pb-16 md:pb-20">
        <ol class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-white/40">
          <li><a href="/fr/" class="hover:text-white/70 transition-colors no-underline">Accueil</a></li>
          <li class="before:content-['/'] before:mx-2"><a href="/fr/#OurServices" class="hover:text-white/70 transition-colors no-underline">Services</a></li>
          <li class="before:content-['/'] before:mx-2 text-white/60">Migration Chine</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>

      <div class="io-grid items-center pb-20 md:pb-28 lg:pb-36">
        <!-- Text: 7 cols -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-6">
            Migration Chine
          </p>
          <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[56px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-white leading-[1.07]">
            Faites entrer votre site en Chine.
            <span class="block mt-2 text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]">Sérieusement.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-8 text-lg text-white/60 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            Une migration vers la Chine, c’est une relance complète du site. On déplace contenu, design et hébergement d’un seul tenant, pour que ce qui sort en ligne fonctionne vraiment auprès du public chinois.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-4 text-base text-white/40 max-w-xl leading-relaxed">
            Vingt ans à Shanghai. Plus de 50 marques internationales migrées, aucune cassée en route.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-10 flex flex-wrap gap-4">
            <Button href="/fr/contact/" variant="primary" size="lg">Parler de votre migration</Button>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Visual: 5 cols, migration status panel -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-4 lg:col-start-9 mt-12 lg:mt-0">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="bg-white/[0.06] backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/10 rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-6">
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
                <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
                <span class="text-xs text-white/30 ml-2 font-mono">statut-migration</span>
              </div>
              <div class="space-y-4">
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between">
                  <span class="text-sm text-white/50">Contenu localisé</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-400 font-mono">100%</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full h-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-2">
                  <span class="text-sm text-white/50">Ressources bloquées</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-400 font-mono">0 / 47</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full h-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="w-full h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-2">
                  <span class="text-sm text-white/50">Temps de chargement</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-400 font-mono">2,1s</span>
                </div>
                <div class="w-full h-1.5 bg-white/10 rounded-full overflow-hidden">
                  <div class="w-[15%] h-full bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-green-400 rounded-full"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex items-center justify-between pt-2">
                  <span class="text-sm text-white/50">Conformité ICP</span>
                  <span class="text-sm font-semibold text-green-400 font-mono">Déposé</span>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Decorative glow -->
            <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/5 rounded-3xl blur-2xl -z-10"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Introduction -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <div class="io-grid items-center gap-y-12">
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[44px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight mb-6">
            La plupart des « migrations Chine » ne règlent que la partie facile.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed mb-5">
            On déplace les fichiers, on change d’hébergeur, on dépose l’ICP. Le site charge. Le taux de rebond, lui, reste à 80 %.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed mb-5">
            Le vrai chantier commence là où le visiteur chinois pose les yeux : titre pensé à Munich, mise en page conçue à Boston, signaux de confiance dont vos équipes mondiales sont fières. Rien de tout cela ne se traduit tout seul.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
            Une vraie migration travaille sur trois couches en même temps. Contenu. UX. Hébergement. Un seul projet, piloté depuis Shanghai.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Visual: phone in hand, scrolling past -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 lg:col-start-8">
          <div class="relative">
            <div class="relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl aspect-[4/5] lg:aspect-[5/6] bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
              <img
                src="/images/migration-easy-problem.webp"
                alt="Une lectrice chinoise fait défiler un site qui charge mais ne lui parle pas"
                class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
                loading="lazy"
                decoding="async"
              />
            </div>
            <!-- Decorative accent -->
            <div class="absolute -inset-3 bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/[0.04] rounded-3xl blur-2xl -z-10"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Layers -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-14">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-4">
          Les trois couches d’une vraie migration
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[48px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight">
          Contenu. UX. Hébergement. Un seul projet.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 lg:gap-6">
        {layers.map((layer) => (
          <article class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 lg:p-10 border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] flex flex-col">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/10 flex items-center justify-center mb-6 flex-shrink-0">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d={layer.iconPath} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-2">
              {layer.label}
            </p>
            <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-snug mb-4">
              {layer.title}
            </h3>
            <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
              {layer.body}
            </p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Migration Scenarios -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mb-14">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-4">
          Scénarios de migration
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[48px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight">
          Trois chemins vers la Chine
        </h2>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
          Chaque migration part d’un point différent. Voici comment nous abordons les trois cas que nous rencontrons le plus souvent.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 lg:gap-6">
        {scenarios.map((scenario) => (
          <article class="group relative flex flex-col p-7 lg:p-8 bg-white rounded-2xl border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] hover:border-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/40 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-[0_12px_32px_rgba(15,15,18,0.06)] transition-all duration-300">
            <!-- Diagram -->
            <div class="mb-6 h-16 flex items-center" aria-hidden="true">
              {scenario.diagram === 'single' && (
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-surface-light)] text-xs font-medium font-[var(--font-button)] text-[var(--color-text-muted)] border border-[var(--color-surface-border)]">Site mondial</span>
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/10 text-xs font-medium font-[var(--font-button)] text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] border border-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/20">中国</span>
                </div>
              )}
              {scenario.diagram === 'swap' && (
                <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-surface-light)] text-xs font-medium font-[var(--font-button)] text-[var(--color-text-muted)] border border-[var(--color-surface-border)] line-through decoration-[var(--color-text-muted)]/40">Ancien CMS</span>
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-text-muted)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-surface-light)] text-xs font-medium font-[var(--font-button)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] border border-[var(--color-surface-border)]">Nouveau CMS</span>
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
                  <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/10 text-xs font-medium font-[var(--font-button)] text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] border border-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/20">中国</span>
                </div>
              )}
              {scenario.diagram === 'parallel' && (
                <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5">
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-surface-light)] text-xs font-medium font-[var(--font-button)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] border border-[var(--color-surface-border)]">Site mondial</span>
                    <span class="text-[var(--color-text-muted)] text-sm">·</span>
                    <span class="px-3 py-1.5 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/10 text-xs font-medium font-[var(--font-button)] text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] border border-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/20">中国</span>
                  </div>
                  <span class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)] font-medium">Une seule chaîne éditoriale</span>
                </div>
              )}
            </div>

            <!-- Timeline pill -->
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 self-start mb-4 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-surface-light)] text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)]">
              <svg class="w-3.5 h-3.5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"/></svg>
              {scenario.timeline}
            </div>

            <h3 class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-snug mb-2">
              {scenario.title}
            </h3>
            <p class="text-base font-semibold text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-snug mb-3">
              {scenario.lead}
            </p>
            <p class="text-[15px] text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed mb-6">
              {scenario.body}
            </p>

            <div class="mt-auto pt-5 border-t border-[var(--color-surface-border)]">
              <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-text-muted)] mb-3">Pour vous si</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2">
                {scenario.fit.map((point) => (
                  <li class="flex items-start gap-2.5 text-[15px] text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
                    <svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-4 h-4 mt-1 text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"/></svg>
                    <span>{point}</span>
                  </li>
                ))}
              </ul>
            </div>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Process: phased -->
  <section class="section-spacing bg-[var(--color-surface-light)]">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <div class="io-grid items-start">
        <!-- Left: sticky heading -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 mb-12 lg:mb-0 lg:sticky lg:top-32">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-4">
            Comment nous menons le projet
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[48px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight">
            Trois phases. Huit étapes. Un lancement.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
            Pensé pour la performance et les habitudes du public chinois dès le premier jour, jamais rafistolé à la fin.
          </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Right: phased steps with vertical timeline -->
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-6 lg:col-start-7 relative">
          <!-- Vertical line -->
          <div class="absolute left-[14px] top-3 bottom-3 w-px bg-[var(--color-surface-border)]" aria-hidden="true"></div>

          <div class="space-y-14">
            {phases.map((phase) => (
              <div class="relative">
                <!-- Phase header with marker on the line -->
                <div class="flex items-center gap-5 mb-6">
                  <div class="relative z-10 flex-shrink-0 w-[30px] h-[30px] rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)] ring-8 ring-white flex items-center justify-center">
                    <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="3" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <div class="flex items-baseline gap-3">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]">
                      {phase.label}
                    </span>
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)]">
                      {phase.title}
                    </h3>
                  </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Steps under the phase, indented past the line -->
                <div class="pl-[50px] space-y-5">
                  {phase.steps.map((step) => (
                    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-5 border border-[var(--color-surface-border)]">
                      <h4 class="text-base lg:text-lg font-semibold font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight mb-2">
                        {step.title}
                      </h4>
                      <p class="text-[15px] text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
                        {step.body}
                      </p>
                    </div>
                  ))}
                </div>
              </div>
            ))}
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Operational Checklist -->
  <section class="relative section-spacing bg-[var(--color-surface-dark)] overflow-hidden">
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -top-40 -right-40 w-[640px] h-[640px] rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/[0.08] blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -bottom-48 -left-40 w-[520px] h-[520px] rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/[0.05] blur-3xl"></div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <!-- Hero row: heading + feature visual -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-12 gap-6 lg:gap-8 items-stretch mb-10 lg:mb-14">
        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-5 flex flex-col">
          <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-4">
            Liste opérationnelle
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[48px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-white leading-[1.05] mb-6">
            Rien d’important ne reste sur le quai.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-white/65 leading-relaxed mb-8">
            Une migration, c’est des dizaines de petites choses qui doivent toutes tomber juste, en même temps. Voici les huit chantiers que nous déplaçons, reconstruisons et vérifions à chaque projet.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-auto inline-flex items-center gap-5 self-start px-5 py-4 rounded-xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md">
            <div class="flex items-baseline gap-1 font-[var(--font-heading)]">
              <span class="text-4xl font-medium text-white leading-none tracking-tight">08</span>
              <span class="text-xl font-medium text-white/30 leading-none">/08</span>
            </div>
            <div class="h-10 w-px bg-white/10"></div>
            <p class="text-xs uppercase tracking-wider text-white/55 leading-snug">
              Chantiers couverts<br />à chaque projet
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="col-span-12 lg:col-span-7">
          <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden border border-white/10 bg-[var(--color-surface-dark)] aspect-[16/10] lg:aspect-auto lg:h-full lg:min-h-[380px]">
            <img
              src="/images/migration-pipeline-architecture.webp"
              alt="Modules d’un site web circulant dans la chaîne de migration"
              loading="lazy"
              decoding="async"
              class="absolute inset-0 w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-tr from-[var(--color-surface-dark)]/40 via-transparent to-transparent"></div>
            <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 ring-1 ring-inset ring-white/5 rounded-2xl"></div>
            <div class="absolute top-5 right-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-surface-dark)]/70 backdrop-blur-md border border-white/10">
              <span class="relative flex h-2 w-2">
                <span class="absolute inline-flex h-full w-full rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)] opacity-60 animate-ping"></span>
                <span class="relative inline-flex rounded-full h-2 w-2 bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]"></span>
              </span>
              <span class="text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-wider text-white/80">Migration en cours</span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Items grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-3 lg:gap-4">
        {migrationItems.map((item, i) => (
          <article class="group relative flex flex-col h-full p-6 lg:p-7 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.04] border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-md transition-all duration-300 hover:bg-white/[0.07] hover:border-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/30 hover:-translate-y-0.5">
            <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-6">
              <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/15 border border-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/25 flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.75" d={item.iconPath} />
                </svg>
              </div>
              <span class="font-mono text-xs text-white/35 tracking-[0.18em] mt-1.5">
                {String(i + 1).padStart(2, '0')}
              </span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-base lg:text-[17px] font-semibold font-[var(--font-heading)] text-white mb-2 leading-snug">
              {item.label}
            </h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-white/55 leading-relaxed">
              {item.body}
            </p>
          </article>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why Different -->
  <section class="section-spacing">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding">
      <div class="text-center mb-16">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-4">
          Pourquoi c’est différent
        </p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[48px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight">
          Une migration vers la Chine joue selon d’autres règles.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 lg:gap-6">
        {challenges.map((item) => (
          <div class="flex gap-5 p-6 lg:p-8 rounded-2xl bg-[var(--color-surface-light)] border border-[var(--color-surface-border)]">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 h-12 rounded-full bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/10 flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-[var(--color-brand-orange)]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" aria-hidden="true">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d={item.iconPath} />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <div class="flex-1">
              <h3 class="text-lg lg:text-xl font-semibold font-[var(--font-heading)] text-[var(--color-text-dark)] leading-tight mb-2">
                {item.title}
              </h3>
              <p class="text-base text-[var(--color-text-body)] leading-relaxed">
                {item.body}
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <WhoIsThisFor heading="Pensé pour les marques qui entrent en Chine" audiences={audiences} background="light" />

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="relative bg-[var(--color-surface-dark)] overflow-hidden py-16 sm:py-20 lg:py-32">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-[600px] h-[300px] bg-[var(--color-brand-orange)]/5 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1400px] section-padding text-center">
      <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-[var(--color-brand-orange)] mb-4">
        Lancer votre migration
      </p>
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-[48px] font-medium font-[var(--font-heading)] text-white leading-tight max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        Vous pensez à faire entrer votre site en Chine ?
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-white/60 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
        Dites-nous où vit le site aujourd’hui, ce qu’il fait pour votre marque, et ce qu’il doit faire pour le public chinois. Nous revenons sous deux jours ouvrés avec une note écrite : périmètre, calendrier, et lecture claire de ce à quoi ressemble une vraie migration pour votre projet. Sans frais, sans engagement.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4">
        <Button href="/fr/contact/" variant="primary" size="lg">Démarrer le cadrage de migration</Button>
        <Button href="/fr/#OurServices" variant="ghost" size="lg" class="!text-white/70 hover:!text-white">Voir nos services</Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</PageLayout>
